Primo's founders are Italian but they are based in Islington, London. They set up a 
Kickstarter campaign last month to fund the Primo kit and needed to 
raise £35,000 by 22 December in order to start selling the device.

The company announced today it is set to reach this target within days but devices won’t be available until August next year.

